// Vendored daily Polymarket bot snapshots live here as YYYY-MM-DD.json.
//
// Schema (loose — extra fields allowed; reader pulls what it needs):
//   {
//     "bankroll": 158.0,            // dollars (USDC + open exposure)
//     "pulled_at": "2026-04-26T14:00:00Z",
//     "positions": [],              // [{ market, outcome, size, avg_price, current_price, exposure_dollars }, ...]
//     "open_orders": []             // [{ market, outcome, side, size, price }, ...]
//   }
//
// To wire daily polymarket snapshots, run
//   polytrader/scripts/dump_polymarket_snapshot.py   (TBD)
// and commit the YYYY-MM-DD.json output to this directory.
//
// Reader: src/lib/snapshots.ts → getLatestPolymarketSnapshot()
// Consumer: src/lib/portfolio-aggregate.ts → buildPrediction()
//
// While this directory contains no YYYY-MM-DD.json files the aggregator
// degrades gracefully to the constant baseline in src/data/prediction.json
// (`polymarket_bankroll`, currently $158).
